es must belong to 18 to 40 years of age.The income of the candidate must be less than Rs. 15,000 per month.He / She must not be an income tax payer.Applicants must not be engaged in organized sector with membership of EPF / NPS / ESICApplicant must have a savings bank account.He / She should possess Aadhar number.PM-SYM scheme 2019 aims to provide minimum assured pension of Rs. 3,000 which will continue life long on attaining the age of 60 years. Check PM Shram Yogi Maan-dhan Yojana Details PDF.PM Shram Yogi Maandhan Yojana (PMSYM) Pension Chart & NotificationBefore making online application for the scheme, candidates must check the PM Shram Yogi Maandhan Yojana (PMSYM) Pension Chart. PMSYM contribution is age specific and govt. is equal partner in the financial security of unorganized sector. This pension chart would show the subscribers the amount of contribution to be made and checked using the link below:- PM Shram Yogi Maandhan Yojana (PMSYM) NotificationCandidates can make further visit at www.labour.gov.in / www.licindia.in/home/index. To find nearest common service center (CSC), visit the official website at www.locator.csccloud.in  Sarkari Yojana App - Download Now  at  "}